        What to Expect When Selling in Teneriffe
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Teneriffe is Brisbane's most distinctive inner-city residential address. The converted woolstore apartments and freestanding homes on the river bend attract a buyer who is making a very deliberate lifestyle choice.
      </p>
    </div>
